<li><a href="https://ocle.uic.edu/project-oasis/project-oasis-guidelines/">Project Oasis Guidelines</a></li>
<li><a href="http://ocle.uic.edu/oasis-use-policy/">Oasis Use Policy</a></li>
<li><a href="https://uofi.box.com/s/w8643q32d10f5jx0ed8kklp2n9rdonof">LSC Webinar Snapshot</a></li>
